title: DeeThree on the Power of Virtual and Physical 3D Technologies
text:
DeeThree on the Power of Virtual and Physical 3D Technologies 19 October 2015 Expand DeeThree co-founder, Peter Davis tells the TCT Show + Personalize 2015 Conference audience how eight-hour Minecraft sessions and a passion for 3D printing turned into a multi-medium 3D data portfolio combining visualisations, 3D printed models, augmented reality and virtual reality. 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel . Tags
